listing.neighborhood_overview:
The location And surrounding are outstanding. Next to the city centre. There are a lot of restaurants And shops nearby And in the evening You can Enjoy the Amstel river from the balkony. So You have Your own terrace.

Van Gogh And Rijksmuseum are within a 10' walk. Also the Nice Zoo Artis is very close by.

The famous nine streets for shopping and the Leidse & Rembrandt square are within a 10' walk too. 

You are here in the middle of everything! 
And if You want rest and mindfullness just walk along the river and Enjoy the beautiful surrounding and typical Dutch buildings.
